subject: Baseball
Playoff Games
lead_paragraph: Dylan Bundy, a 6-foot-1 right-hander who was the fourth pick of the 2011 draft, made his Camden Yards debut on Tuesday night, pitching a scoreless ninth in a 4-0 loss to the Blue Jays.
